---
// Cinematic full-bleed feature section spotlighting the two
// consecutive game-design internships at 505 Games / Avantgarden
// in Milan, working on Among the Trolls. Lives on the landing page.
---

<section class="milan" id="milan" aria-labelledby="milan-heading">
  <div class="milan__backdrop" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/images/att.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
    <div class="milan__scrim"></div>
    <div class="milan__grain"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="milan__content">
    <p class="milan__kicker">
      <span class="milan__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      // 2024 — 2025 · milano, it
    </p>

    <h2 id="milan-heading" class="milan__title">
      Two summers in <em>Milan.</em>
    </h2>

    <p class="milan__lede">
      Two consecutive game-design internships at
      <strong>505 Games / Avantgarden</strong>, shipping systems for
      <em>Among the Trolls</em> — a first-person survival adventure.
      Worked fully in Italian. Relocated both summers.
    </p>

    <div class="milan__cards">
      <article class="milan-card">
        <header class="milan-card__head">
          <p class="milan-card__year">Summer 2024</p>
          <span class="milan-card__tag">first run</span>
        </header>
        <h3 class="milan-card__title">Game Design Intern</h3>
        <p class="milan-card__org">505 Games · Avantgarden · Milan</p>
        <ul class="milan-card__list">
          <li>Prototyped building and magic mechanics in UE5 — placement rules, decision logic, and visual feedback</li>
          <li>Built 3 dungeon prototype levels from modular UE5 pieces with smart wall and door behaviors</li>
          <li>Authored ~7 Confluence specs with flowcharts and edge cases for engineering handoff</li>
          <li>QA on <em>Brothers: A Tale of Two Sons Remake</em> — frame-drop bug with video repro</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="milan-card__photos">
          <div class="milan-card__photo">
            <img src="/images/lucamilan.jpg" alt="Milan, summer 2024" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="milan-card milan-card--accent">
        <header class="milan-card__head">
          <p class="milan-card__year">Summer 2025</p>
          <span class="milan-card__tag">encore</span>
        </header>
        <h3 class="milan-card__title">Game Design Intern</h3>
        <p class="milan-card__org">505 Games · Avantgarden · Milan</p>
        <ul class="milan-card__list">
          <li>Owned quest and dialogue flow via the Narrative plugin — 12+ quests and 12+ dialogue sequences with event-driven triggers</li>
          <li>Broke down feature work in Jira and aligned weekly priorities with design leads</li>
          <li>Designed interaction flows and annotated mechanics in Figma for review and engineering handoff</li>
          <li>Collaborated daily in <em>Italian</em> across design, engineering, and QA</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="milan-card__photos">
          <div class="milan-card__photo">
            <img src="/images/505-summer-2025.jpg" alt="Milan, summer 2025" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <footer class="milan__foot">
      <span class="milan__chip">Fluent Italian</span>
      <span class="milan__chip">UE5 · Confluence · Jira · Perforce</span>
      <span class="milan__credit">
        // Among the Trolls · Avantgarden / 505 Games
      </span>
    </footer>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .milan {
    position: relative;
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
    min-height: clamp(640px, 82vh, 920px);
    display: grid;
    align-items: center;
    padding: clamp(60px, 10vw, 140px) clamp(28px, 6vw, 96px);
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
    color: #fff5e8;
    scroll-margin-top: 90px;
  }

  /* ------------------------------------------------------------------
     Backdrop: photo + dark scrim + subtle grain
  ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
  .milan__backdrop {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .milan__backdrop img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    filter: saturate(0.85) contrast(1.05) brightness(0.72);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  .milan__scrim {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        100deg,
        rgba(6, 8, 20, 0.92) 0%,
        rgba(6, 8, 20, 0.78) 38%,
        rgba(6, 8, 20, 0.42) 68%,
        rgba(6, 8, 20, 0.18) 100%
      ),
      radial-gradient(
        ellipse at 20% 70%,
        rgba(255, 120, 60, 0.18) 0%,
        transparent 50%
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .milan__grain {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      0deg,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 0 1px,
      transparent 1px 3px
    );
    mix-blend-mode: overlay;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ------------------------------------------------------------------
     Content
  ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
  .milan__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1180px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(20px, 3vw, 36px);
  }

  .milan__kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.78);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .milan__dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ff7a3d;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 122, 61, 0.18),
      0 0 18px rgba(255, 122, 61, 0.6);
    animation: milan-pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes milan-pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
    50%      { transform: scale(1.25); opacity: 0.7; }
  }

  .milan__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 40, "wght" 500;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 6.6rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 16ch;
    color: #fff5e8;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .milan__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 100, "wght" 500;
    color: #ffb78a;
  }

  .milan__lede {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.55vw, 1.3rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 60ch;
    color: rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.92);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .milan__lede strong {
    color: #fff5e8;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .milan__lede em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #ffb78a;
  }

  /* ------------------------------------------------------------------
     Cards
  ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
  .milan__cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(16px, 2vw, 28px);
    margin-top: clamp(8px, 2vw, 20px);
  }

  .milan-card {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: rgba(10, 12, 24, 0.68);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(120%);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(120%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.14);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: clamp(20px, 2.6vw, 32px);
    transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1),
                border-color 0.3s ease,
                box-shadow 0.35s ease;
  }

  .milan-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(255, 183, 138, 0.45);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px -20px rgba(255, 120, 60, 0.35);
  }

  .milan-card--accent {
    border-color: rgba(255, 183, 138, 0.28);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 183, 138, 0.08) inset;
  }

  .milan-card__head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .milan-card__year {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #ffb78a;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .milan-card__tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.55);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.22);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .milan-card__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72, "SOFT" 30, "wght" 500;
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2vw, 1.75rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    color: #fff5e8;
  }

  .milan-card__org {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.6);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }

  .milan-card__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .milan-card__list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.88);
  }

  .milan-card__list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.55em;
    width: 10px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #ff7a3d;
  }

  .milan-card__list em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #ffb78a;
  }

  /* ------------------------------------------------------------------
     Photo strip (2 placeholders per card)
  ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
  .milan-card__photos {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .milan-card__photo {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.22);
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.04) 0 8px,
        rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.015) 8px 16px
      );
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .milan-card__photo::after {
    content: "// photo";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.38);
  }

  .milan-card__photo img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .milan-card__photo:has(img) {
    border-style: solid;
    border-color: rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.18);
    background: #0a0c18;
  }

  .milan-card__photo:has(img)::after {
    display: none;
  }

  .milan-card--accent .milan-card__photo {
    border-color: rgba(255, 183, 138, 0.3);
  }

  .milan-card--accent .milan-card__photo::after {
    color: rgba(255, 183, 138, 0.55);
  }

  .milan-card:hover .milan-card__photo {
    border-color: rgba(255, 183, 138, 0.4);
  }

  /* ------------------------------------------------------------------
     Footer
  ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
  .milan__foot {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: clamp(12px, 2vw, 24px);
  }

  .milan__chip {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 183, 138, 0.4);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: #ffb78a;
    background: rgba(255, 122, 61, 0.08);
  }

  .milan__credit {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 245, 232, 0.5);
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  /* ------------------------------------------------------------------
     Responsive
  ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .milan {
      padding: clamp(56px, 12vw, 96px) clamp(20px, 6vw, 32px);
      min-height: auto;
    }
    .milan__cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .milan__credit {
      margin-left: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .milan__dot {
      animation: none !important;
    }
  }
</style>
